      <lg type="song lyrics">
        <head>Gourmet</head>
        <lg number="1" type="stanza">
          <l>Delicious indeed you are to me </l>
          <l>Once in a while I allow myself </l>
          <l>The pleasure of you </l>
          <l>Good for the skin, I will have you from within </l>
          <l>As I become a thief </l>
          <l>Delicious indeed you are to me </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="2" type="stanza">
          <l>You taste so good </l>
          <l>Though I know I should </l>
          <l>Not get used to the fancy style of you </l>
          <l>To the fancy style </l>
        </lg>
        <lg number="3" type="stanza">
          <l>Addicted indeed your flesh to me </l>
          <l>Too many times I was drown to my baby delight </l>
          <l>The price is high </l>
          <l>I will pay it and then cry </l>
          <l>Forbidden and so far</l>
        </lg>
      </lg>
